    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We propose an augmented version of the traditional SIRD epidemic model and we estimate its parameters using the SaRs-Cov-2 Italian open-data. The model\u2019s parameters are estimated partly using numerical optimization and partly with ABC. Our estimation procedure provides a good fit to real data.</jats:p>",
